### 2 · Homepage Redesign

#### [MODIFY] [Home.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/Home.tsx)

Complete rewrite with 7 sections:

**Section 1 — Hero (full viewport)**
- Animated gradient background with subtle marble-texture overlay
- Large MIYAR logo with Arabic مِعيار subtitle
- Tagline: "Design Intelligence for UAE Luxury Real Estate"
- Animated floating stats (578K+ DLD Transactions, 150+ Benchmarks, 38 Compliance)
- Two CTAs: "Get Started" (gold solid) + "Watch Demo" (outlined)
