**Section 2 — Feature Showcase (6 cards)**
- Glassmorphism cards in 3×2 grid (responsive: 1col mobile, 2col tablet)
- Cards: AI Design Brief, Live Cost Calculator, Investor PDF Export, MIYAR Score, Market Intelligence, Sustainability Compliance
- Hover animations: scale + glow + icon pulse
- Each card shows a mini-preview image (generated via generate_image tool)

**Section 3 — How It Works (4 steps)**
- Horizontal timeline with animated connecting lines
- Steps: Define Project → AI Analysis → Review & Compare → Export & Share
- Each step has an animated icon and description
- Number circles with gold gradient

**Section 4 — App Preview**
- Dashboard screenshot in a 3D perspective frame with drop shadow
- Floating annotation cards pointing to key features
- "See it in action" caption with fade-in animation

**Section 5 — UAE Market Data Badge**
- Trust signals: "Powered by DLD Transaction Data", "Estidama & Al Sa'fat Certified", "RICS NRM Aligned"
