- Expandable feature lists per version
- Latest version highlighted with gold border and "Current" badge

**Section 7 — Footer**
- Premium footer with gold MIYAR logo
- "Powered by Gemini AI + Live UAE Market Data"
- Links: Methodology, Privacy, Terms, Contact
- Social/contact info

